1
00:00:01,300 --> 00:00:03,540
The 88 Stars of the Heavens.

2
00:00:04,880 --> 00:00:05,520
Shine!

3
00:00:05,520 --> 00:00:07,610
Urano Meteoria!

4
00:00:17,680 --> 00:00:25,670
If it's love and dreams and you it'll become magical.

5
00:00:25,670 --> 00:00:32,840
Now, let's cast a smile spell!

6
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:45,770
I kind of admired this powerful world,

7
00:00:45,770 --> 00:00:50,190
chock-full of problems.

8
00:00:51,110 --> 00:00:56,970
Frozen time has started to move again

9
00:00:56,970 --> 00:01:02,580
ever since I met you.

10
00:01:02,580 --> 00:01:08,000
Why were we born? Why do we live?

11
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:13,840
I don't need any complicated answers.

12
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:19,780
Laugh! Cry! Be honest with yourself.

13
00:01:19,780 --> 00:01:24,560
Simple feelings are the most important.

14
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:32,900
You can change those tears shed on sad nights into strength.

15
00:01:32,900 --> 00:01:39,530
Now, let's cast a smile spell!

16
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:54,460
Huh? What was I...

17
00:01:55,050 --> 00:01:56,700
What happened?

18
00:01:59,020 --> 00:02:01,280
Hibiki! Happy!

19
00:02:01,650 --> 00:02:03,310
Oh right, Natsu!

20
00:02:10,620 --> 00:02:13,650
I... won't... lose...

21
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:20,450
Oracion Seis... doesn't lose...

22
00:02:24,010 --> 00:02:25,940
Recollections of Jellal.

23
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:31,540
What is this...

24
00:02:31,540 --> 00:02:34,570
It's like I have no power at all...

25
00:02:34,570 --> 00:02:38,670
And hey... Why is she so beat up?

26
00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:40,840
One woman, one kill!

27
00:02:42,090 --> 00:02:43,470
Blast away to oblivion!

28
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,430
It missed?

29
00:02:49,140 --> 00:02:50,580
You too?!

30
00:02:59,430 --> 00:03:00,490
Natsu!

31
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,720
My prayer...

32
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,960
My prayer...

33
00:03:17,930 --> 00:03:19,670
To disappear into the sky...

34
00:03:22,050 --> 00:03:25,440
...like an angel...

35
00:03:29,470 --> 00:03:31,310
I said sky, not water!

36
00:03:32,580 --> 00:03:34,020
Natsu!

37
00:03:36,690 --> 00:03:38,540
Get it together!

38
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:42,150
Hold out your hand, Natsu!

39
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,780
What the... Rapids?

40
00:03:57,230 --> 00:04:01,380
Hold it a sec... You've got to be kidding me!

41
00:04:16,770 --> 00:04:17,740
Natsu!

42
00:04:27,550 --> 00:04:29,330
I-Impossible...

43
00:04:29,660 --> 00:04:31,790
Even Angel has fallen?

44
00:04:33,330 --> 00:04:36,350
Your death will not be in vain!

45
00:04:36,910 --> 00:04:40,310
The extinction of the light will begin soon!

46
00:04:45,770 --> 00:04:47,190
I'm not dead, buddy.

47
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:08,040
Jellal is alive?

48
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,130
But how?

49
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:18,340
And wait... Why is he here?

50
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:23,020
Erza...

51
00:05:25,230 --> 00:05:29,380
Erza, there is no such thing 
as freedom in this world.

52
00:05:30,230 --> 00:05:31,830
Let Erza go!

53
00:05:33,110 --> 00:05:37,730
I don't know... I don't know 
how I should face him...

54
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,490
My heavens...

55
00:05:43,490 --> 00:05:48,340
You say that Nirvana is a magic that 
can change people's personality?

56
00:05:48,340 --> 00:05:50,660
Exactly! Yes...

57
00:05:51,450 --> 00:05:55,150
The first stage is that black light,

58
00:05:55,150 --> 00:05:59,680
which forcibly changes anyone trapped 
in the boundary between good and evil.

59
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,720
Yes...

60
00:06:01,470 --> 00:06:06,150
Which means that you were in 
the gap between good and evil?

61
00:06:06,150 --> 00:06:11,670
I felt like I was doing something a bit 
wrong in the name of earning money.

62
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:13,350
Yes...

63
00:06:13,350 --> 00:06:15,930
You seemed pretty happy about it to me.

64
00:06:16,430 --> 00:06:20,310
It was all for my long-lost brother...

65
00:06:24,850 --> 00:06:27,530
All to search for my brother!

66
00:06:28,500 --> 00:06:31,180
It was for that I wanted money!

67
00:06:31,180 --> 00:06:32,150
Yes...

68
00:06:34,660 --> 00:06:38,640
When I look at you, I remember the past...

69
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:42,900
Could it be... Are you saying I 
resemble your brother, perhaps?

70
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:47,170
You are the spitting image of the 
potatoes my brother used to eat!

71
00:06:47,170 --> 00:06:48,670
Potato head?!

72
00:06:48,670 --> 00:06:52,910
Now, let's stop Brain and the others 
for the sake of love! Yes...

73
00:06:52,910 --> 00:06:54,530
R-Right...

74
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:58,110
What's wrong?

75
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:00,600
What the heck has been going on?

76
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,060
None of my magic has...

77
00:07:02,940 --> 00:07:03,890
Damn it!

78
00:07:04,230 --> 00:07:07,230
Air Magic, Aerial Shot!

79
00:07:11,050 --> 00:07:12,540
I missed again?

80
00:07:15,070 --> 00:07:16,230
Goddamn it!

81
00:07:17,140 --> 00:07:19,520
But... why?

82
00:07:22,230 --> 00:07:23,330
That makes two.

83
00:07:24,210 --> 00:07:28,230
How boring. Isn't there anyone stronger?

84
00:07:35,370 --> 00:07:38,390
I wonder if I shouldn't have come?

85
00:07:38,650 --> 00:07:41,780
Are you still saying that, Wendy?

86
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:42,930
Well...

87
00:07:43,310 --> 00:07:47,570
Those negative feelings will get 
your heart stolen by the darkness.

88
00:07:47,890 --> 00:07:52,490
But I ran away leaving Lucy-san 
and the others, right?

89
00:07:53,030 --> 00:07:56,430
That's because you wouldn't 
have been any help regardless.

90
00:07:57,940 --> 00:07:59,900
I knew it, I'm just...

91
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:04,150
But without you here, Erza would be dead now.

92
00:08:04,660 --> 00:08:05,260
Yeah...

93
00:08:06,630 --> 00:08:09,680
But we weren't able to find Nirvana either.

94
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,530
I wonder...

95
00:08:11,530 --> 00:08:15,850
You were happy to be able to 
meet that Jellal person, right?

96
00:08:15,850 --> 00:08:17,070
But that's...

97
00:08:17,430 --> 00:08:20,670
So what is with Jellal?

98
00:08:20,910 --> 00:08:23,180
You said he saved your life,

99
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:26,540
but I've never heard anything about that.

100
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:30,190
Oh, yeah... I never told you, did I?

101
00:08:31,190 --> 00:08:33,300
It was seven years ago...

102
00:08:34,420 --> 00:08:37,340
The Sky Dragon, Grandine, vanished.

103
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:41,320
And I was wandering along the road...

104
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:46,670
Grandine... Where are you, Grandine?

105
00:09:10,910 --> 00:09:11,940
What's the matter?

106
00:09:12,300 --> 00:09:13,530
She's gone...

107
00:09:13,530 --> 00:09:14,190
What?

108
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:17,830
She disappeared!

109
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:24,050
That was how we met.

110
00:09:24,050 --> 00:09:28,730
He was in the middle of traveling, 
and told me that he was lost as well.

111
00:09:36,740 --> 00:09:42,050
So for the next month, we continued 
traveling together with no destination in mind...

112
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:53,040
Jellal!

113
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:58,350
Even on a nasty day like 
this, some good can come.

114
00:09:58,700 --> 00:09:59,530
See?

115
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,890
Where did you pick them?

116
00:10:02,890 --> 00:10:04,030
Don't ask...

117
00:10:04,850 --> 00:10:06,330
Now, let's eat.

118
00:10:06,330 --> 00:10:06,840
Yeah!

119
00:10:27,450 --> 00:10:28,670
Wait here a second.

120
00:10:35,020 --> 00:10:36,320
Thank you...

121
00:10:45,450 --> 00:10:47,490
Where are we going now?

122
00:10:47,490 --> 00:10:49,960
I don't know... Where would be nice?

123
00:10:51,190 --> 00:10:54,060
Can I tag along with you forever?

124
00:10:54,300 --> 00:10:55,300
Of course.

125
00:10:59,710 --> 00:11:03,090
But one day, he said something 
weird all of a sudden...

126
00:11:04,810 --> 00:11:05,730
Anima!

127
00:11:05,730 --> 00:11:07,790
Huh? What's the matter?

128
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:15,580
No! I wanna come with you!

129
00:11:15,580 --> 00:11:18,070
You can't. It'll be dangerous if you come.

130
00:11:18,070 --> 00:11:22,700
But why? I don't want to leave you, Jellal!

131
00:11:24,300 --> 00:11:26,650
If you head past this 
forest, there's a guild.

132
00:11:26,950 --> 00:11:28,950
They'll take care of you there.

133
00:11:28,950 --> 00:11:30,030
No!

134
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,960
Wendy...

135
00:11:31,960 --> 00:11:34,080
No!

136
00:11:38,530 --> 00:11:42,380
But in the end, I was taken in by the guild,

137
00:11:42,380 --> 00:11:44,380
and that was Caitshelter...

138
00:11:44,380 --> 00:11:46,910
Then, what happened to Jellal?

139
00:11:46,910 --> 00:11:48,900
I never met him afterwards.

140
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:50,750
But I heard rumors later...

141
00:11:50,750 --> 00:11:53,710
About how a council member 
that looked just like Jellal

142
00:11:53,710 --> 00:11:57,690
had done a bunch of really 
bad things recently.

143
00:11:58,320 --> 00:12:01,460
But he was really nice back then!

144
00:12:02,790 --> 00:12:07,100
I wonder if Jellal remembers me?

145
00:12:43,530 --> 00:12:46,190
Erza? She was revived?

146
00:12:46,700 --> 00:12:47,840
Damn it!

147
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,910
How is it that I didn't 
notice she was so close?!

148
00:12:50,830 --> 00:12:54,940
I won't let you interfere until the 
main body of Nirvana starts up!

149
00:12:56,490 --> 00:12:57,780
Jellal...

150
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:00,460
Erza...

151
00:13:02,040 --> 00:13:04,300
Why are you here?

152
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:06,550
I don't know.

153
00:13:08,330 --> 00:13:09,410
Erza...

154
00:13:12,260 --> 00:13:13,850
Er...za...

155
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:20,480
I don't remember anything except that word...

156
00:13:22,610 --> 00:13:26,800
Will you tell me? Who am I?

157
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:30,480
Do you know?

158
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:33,360
Who is Erza?

159
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:36,650
I can't remember anything!

160
00:13:39,450 --> 00:13:42,550
He's lost all his memories?

161
00:13:43,970 --> 00:13:45,450
Jellal...

162
00:13:56,060 --> 00:13:58,170
What was that for, Gray?!

163
00:13:58,170 --> 00:14:00,250
Carla, stand back!

164
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:04,130
Leave everything to me! I'll save Natsu!

165
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:06,950
Wait, no one's here...

166
00:14:06,950 --> 00:14:08,940
What happened?

167
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:14,230
I can't remember anything!

168
00:14:16,870 --> 00:14:19,960
He's lost all his memories?

169
00:14:26,710 --> 00:14:27,550
Jellal...

170
00:14:28,670 --> 00:14:29,380
Stay back!

171
00:14:35,380 --> 00:14:36,060
Stay back...

172
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:39,440
Then you come to me!

173
00:14:40,370 --> 00:14:41,830
For I am Erza!

174
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:43,900
Come here.

175
00:14:46,510 --> 00:14:48,450
Your name is Jellal.

176
00:14:49,380 --> 00:14:51,400
You were once my friend.

177
00:14:53,010 --> 00:14:54,120
Friend?

178
00:14:55,130 --> 00:15:01,350
But you went mad, desecrated 
the dead, hurt your friends,

179
00:15:01,350 --> 00:15:03,190
and even destroyed the Magic Council.

180
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:06,840
You killed Simon.

181
00:15:10,030 --> 00:15:11,100
If you...

182
00:15:12,300 --> 00:15:14,990
If you are trying to say you forgot that,

183
00:15:14,990 --> 00:15:18,320
then I will thrust a blade into your 
chest and engrave it into your heart!

184
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,390
Come here!

185
00:15:19,390 --> 00:15:21,190
Come before me!

186
00:15:24,810 --> 00:15:25,620
I...

187
00:15:26,440 --> 00:15:27,520
To my friends...

188
00:15:28,530 --> 00:15:29,530
No...

189
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:36,590
What have I done?

190
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:41,380
What... What should I...

191
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:47,000
Is this really that Jellal?

192
00:16:01,950 --> 00:16:02,730
Ouch...

193
00:16:03,050 --> 00:16:04,770
Huh? A bandage?

194
00:16:05,710 --> 00:16:07,610
And wait, what's with these clothes?

195
00:16:07,610 --> 00:16:10,500
They are items from the Spirit World.

196
00:16:10,500 --> 00:16:12,200
As yours were quite in tatters...

197
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,360
Virgo!

198
00:16:15,700 --> 00:16:17,700
Where are we?

199
00:16:17,700 --> 00:16:20,000
I gave Natsu-sama a matching outfit.

200
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,360
That <i>really</i> isn't necessary!

201
00:16:21,630 --> 00:16:24,390
Jellal! Where's that light?

202
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:31,520
It's close. And wait, 
hasn't the color changed?

203
00:16:31,520 --> 00:16:36,130
Yes. While you two were unconscious, 
it changed from black to white.

204
00:16:45,420 --> 00:16:47,520
That was a close call. Thanks.

205
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:50,710
What's with you all of a sudden...

206
00:16:50,710 --> 00:16:52,590
He llllikes you!

207
00:16:52,590 --> 00:16:54,400
Would you quit it with that?!

208
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:56,350
Oh yeah, where's Happy?

209
00:16:56,350 --> 00:16:57,710
I have not seen him.

210
00:16:58,040 --> 00:17:01,170
Lucy, weren't you with Erza?

211
00:17:01,170 --> 00:17:02,770
We all got separated.

212
00:17:03,150 --> 00:17:06,930
Oh, well... I guess the two of us 
should head to that light ourselves.

213
00:17:06,930 --> 00:17:09,460
Princess, I will now take my leave.

214
00:17:10,420 --> 00:17:11,370
Virgo!

215
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:16,470
Virgo just passed through the 
gate using her own magic...

216
00:17:17,230 --> 00:17:20,640
Wait, do I have zero magic power left?

217
00:17:28,370 --> 00:17:29,400
Sherry!

218
00:17:31,060 --> 00:17:33,680
Thank goodness you're safe!

219
00:17:34,060 --> 00:17:37,560
It's you! Weren't you on Galuna Island...

220
00:17:37,560 --> 00:17:39,830
Oh yeah, where's doggy and 'brows?

221
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:41,880
Do you know how many episodes back that was?!

222
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:45,570
I found you, Fairy Tail wizards...

223
00:17:45,570 --> 00:17:46,390
What?

224
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:52,090
You idiot!

225
00:17:56,320 --> 00:17:57,260
Gray!

226
00:17:57,650 --> 00:17:59,250
You guys safe?

227
00:17:59,250 --> 00:18:02,530
Let me go! Damn you! You're still alive?

228
00:18:02,530 --> 00:18:04,400
I'm getting revenge for Lyon-sama!

229
00:18:04,400 --> 00:18:08,380
She's been acting all weird 
after that light appeared.

230
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:10,990
You were acting pretty weird before too!

231
00:18:10,990 --> 00:18:11,490
Huh?

232
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:13,900
Natsu, that was a fake...

233
00:18:13,900 --> 00:18:17,500
I won't forgive you! Revenge for Lyon-sama!

234
00:18:17,500 --> 00:18:19,400
Revenge for who exactly?

235
00:18:21,250 --> 00:18:23,370
Reports of my death are greatly exaggerated.

236
00:18:24,130 --> 00:18:25,300
Lyon-sama?

237
00:18:25,830 --> 00:18:27,750
He's a stubborn one.

238
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:31,180
Well, it was pretty close...

239
00:18:31,530 --> 00:18:34,840
That guy's bomb lacrima was 
more powerful than I thought.

240
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:38,840
It took a long time before 
I was able to move again.

241
00:18:38,840 --> 00:18:40,810
Yup, he's stubborn all right.

242
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:44,380
Well, I'm not as stubborn as this guy.

243
00:18:44,380 --> 00:18:45,640
Say what?!

244
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,020
You jump down his throat for <i>that</i>?

245
00:18:51,170 --> 00:18:52,930
Thank... goodness...

246
00:18:54,940 --> 00:18:56,290
What's this?

247
00:18:56,290 --> 00:18:58,810
As I thought, she was 
taken over by something...

248
00:19:01,790 --> 00:19:04,550
That's Nirvana...

249
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:13,170
The black pillar has turned white!

250
00:19:13,570 --> 00:19:15,510
I wonder what's happening?

251
00:19:18,200 --> 00:19:21,370
Hibiki, wake up already!

252
00:19:21,650 --> 00:19:24,220
I hope everyone is okay...

253
00:19:26,560 --> 00:19:29,220
Natsu... Erza...

254
00:19:32,560 --> 00:19:36,110
Okay, I get that you don't remember anything.

255
00:19:36,500 --> 00:19:39,610
No wonder I wasn't able to 
hear your thoughts at all...

256
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:41,820
Oracion Seis!

257
00:19:43,950 --> 00:19:46,440
How'd you manage to get here?

258
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:50,330
And why did you unlock Nirvana's seal?

259
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:56,630
I heard someone's voice while I was asleep.

260
00:19:57,470 --> 00:19:59,830
It said, "We are going to obtain Nirvana."

261
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:03,970
I dimly remembered the place 
where that magic was hidden.

262
00:20:05,610 --> 00:20:10,370
This is a dangerous magic. It 
can't fall into anyone's hands.

263
00:20:11,470 --> 00:20:16,860
And that's why I released the 
seal... To destroy it completely.

264
00:20:17,610 --> 00:20:19,910
To destroy Nirvana?

265
00:20:20,910 --> 00:20:24,150
I've already set up the magic 
circle of self-destruction.

266
00:20:24,460 --> 00:20:27,710
Nirvana will shortly destroy itself.

267
00:20:37,070 --> 00:20:40,010
What the heck is this 
high-level magic circle?

268
00:20:40,850 --> 00:20:44,180
At this rate, Nirvana will be destroyed!

269
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:48,980
Jellal! Spit out the cancellation code!

270
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:53,470
Erza...

271
00:20:53,880 --> 00:20:57,020
I can feel the kindness from that name...

272
00:21:02,190 --> 00:21:07,270
I can feel kindness, 
cheerfulness, and warmth...

273
00:21:10,320 --> 00:21:13,070
I'm sure you'll continue to hate me...

274
00:21:13,710 --> 00:21:17,290
But I can't help that... It's only natural.

275
00:21:19,670 --> 00:21:23,690
But hatred will steal the 
freedom from your heart.

276
00:21:24,010 --> 00:21:26,030
It will eat away at you from within...

277
00:21:29,030 --> 00:21:30,150
You...

278
00:21:35,150 --> 00:21:37,330
I can't go that far...

279
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:40,760
I can't go before you!

280
00:21:40,760 --> 00:21:42,310
He's...

281
00:21:44,290 --> 00:21:49,280
You will be free from Jellal...

282
00:21:50,840 --> 00:21:58,420
I will take your hatred 
and sadness... with me...

283
00:22:00,550 --> 00:22:04,750
He's attached a magic circle of 
self-destruction to his own body?!

284
00:22:08,640 --> 00:22:11,790
You are... free!

285
00:22:17,930 --> 00:22:20,290
Jellal!

286
00:23:55,620 --> 00:23:58,920
What'll we do? Nirvana has been resurrected!

287
00:23:58,920 --> 00:24:00,600
And it's got legs!

288
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:02,570
So Nirvana was actually an octopus?

289
00:24:02,570 --> 00:24:04,320
It's not an octopus, duh!

290
00:24:04,320 --> 00:24:06,020
Then, a squid?

291
00:24:06,020 --> 00:24:07,540
Fine, squid, whatever.

292
00:24:07,540 --> 00:24:09,630
Can we stop squidding around and go already?

293
00:24:09,630 --> 00:24:11,130
Happy...

294
00:24:11,130 --> 00:24:13,100
I think you got the wrong show!

295
00:24:13,100 --> 00:24:13,940
Huh?

296
00:24:13,940 --> 00:24:16,510
Next time: March of Destruction!

297
00:24:17,050 --> 00:24:19,250
That's not what I was trying to...

298
00:24:19,510 --> 00:24:20,670
Don't deny it!

299
00:24:20,670 --> 00:24:21,850
I thought it was awesome!

300
00:24:21,850 --> 00:24:24,140
I think I'll leave him here and go by myself.

301
00:24:24,140 --> 00:24:26,370


